TrackYourDose app was developed by Germany-based firm esooka . 
  The £1 . 
 49 iOS app keeps a record of a user’s personal radiation including exposure from changes in location and flights . 
  It uses a mathematical model developed by scientists and meteorologists and uses a model of cosmic radiation from flight . 
  The app tracks radiation from medical examinations, changes in your location and changes in solar activity . 
 